title: Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez release new song together
text:
An unexpected track appeared on OVO Sound Radio Saturday evening.
According to E! , the song features both Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez. The song is titled "Strong," which appears to address the duo's past relationship.
This is the first time the two have recorded a song together.
